Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.11,0:00:22.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.82,0:00:31.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠 注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.31,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 我如此 三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線 便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.02,0:00:56.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.61,0:00:59.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.78,0:01:06.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.87,0:01:13.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有 Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.38,0:01:19.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 命中的良人就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.80,0:01:26.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠 一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.52,0:01:35.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠 一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.68,0:22:34.76,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.05,0:22:43.40,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此悽涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.03,0:22:50.88,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:22:59.76,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.13,0:23:08.23,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.52,0:23:16.84,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.76,0:23:26.51,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.90,0:23:35.13,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南今天突破一百集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的初戀曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.60,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻有著成人的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.00,0:01:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初戀情人回憶事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要你特地的到新一家裏去打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 反正我們也剛好閒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可有事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然也把我算進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果不適時打掃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏真的要變成鬼屋了 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有一個像小蘭你這麼細心的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一這小子的運氣還真是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.48,0:02:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要把這麼大的房子全部都打掃一遍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天能做多少就先做多少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你打算在這裏耗上一整天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 好好一個週末天氣又這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我園子幹嘛非要來到新一家裏來幫忙打掃不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛管他這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又何必去向博士借鑰匙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我想這裏已經積灰成塔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人打掃太吃力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 你要掃地之前要先把書架的灰塵撢下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 打掃都要從上面開始嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 掃地的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要順著磁磚的紋路才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭你怎麼像老年人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代的女孩子都會自己走出去找男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然為了那個推理狂來這裏當清潔婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底招誰惹誰了 真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起這個初戀嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道新一的初戀情人會是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別瞞我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一一定談過一兩個戀愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這個人在這方面不但遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又耐不住性子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一比人家強的就是他媽媽是電視演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭你從小時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就一直跟那個傢伙在一起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你雖然很溫柔 力氣卻不小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 搞不好新一的初戀就是你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是青梅竹馬經常在一起玩而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說說你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 你的初戀情人就是新一對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你不要亂牽紅線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這副模樣 我是猜對了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千面郎君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再不節制點我可要生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨 當然只有可能是新一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 笨的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他進自家裏何必按門鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是從博士那裏知道我們在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嚇唬我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但新一沒有跟我說他最近打算回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害羞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去接心上人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是你的初戀情人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡思亂想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是工藤的朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個人好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.47,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 難道你是麻美學姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 你認識她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我們在帝丹中學一年級時候的學生會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來工藤因為案子不在家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪每次打電話都是電話錄音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.05,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓你來幫我們一起打掃房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係 反正我也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了學姐 你找新一有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大學推理研究社的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說這個星期週末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.34,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想借幢別墅讓大家為我慶生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望可以請工藤學弟過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我帝丹中學足球部的學弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我很久以前就已經寄信通知他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在離開之前有沒有說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特別說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 完全忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我本來一直以為他一定可以去參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他大概已經忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前的那段告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會忘記也不是沒道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初戀總是會褪色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是新一的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我的觀察果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的時候大家都在傳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說有個一年級的小鬼去找麻美學姐搭訕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不自量力的就是工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼搭訕 那是謠言啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是想向我告白而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.67,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然新一哥哥沒有回來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要不要請別人去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你看我們怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別看我們這樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經靠我們的推理解決過案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子我們說不定可以認識幾個不錯的東京男生哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 如果女孩子來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些男生一定會很歡迎才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 只要請我們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個人一定也會跟著去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 你該不會是在想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是大家說的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我參加東都大學推理研究社的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群孩子餐風露宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不能答應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我們才請爸爸一起去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是大忙人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有那麼多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 叔叔身為名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算到了週末也沒有辦法出去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 毛利小五郎這個名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於推理研究社的會員而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是天神屆臨一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家一定非常矚目大偵探親口說出來的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這次會去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有得過東都小姐的內田麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女更是一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東都小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然叔叔這麼忙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只好放棄這個念頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.59,0:09:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要稍微安排一下工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以監護人的身份出席好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓那些具有潛力的推理研究社的會員失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去解決的那些案例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他們來說 只要能夠達到一丁點作用的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫點忙 或許是一個名偵探該做的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真像個透明人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面寫的別墅在哪兒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是公車站牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就得往右上方走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能見到東都小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是東都大學的男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太榮幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我竟然能夠跟東都大學的這些年輕學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在這裏喝酒談心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且幾位都是有學問的帥哥美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探果然不同凡响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瞭解怎麼利用言詞來達到控制人心的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這個人不是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花花公子 澤井同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都聽說了 部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你最近把一個一年級學妹惹哭了 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們今天可是要幫麻美慶生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們拿我開刀是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.20,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 而且前幾天她寫的小說還得到新人獎的殊榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好可以一起慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呀 森本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小說其實也一直有比到決賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美是我們社裏最受期望的新人 這次敗給她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到輸呢 我在文學院的網球大會裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也輸給她們的二人組了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人家在一年級就當選上東都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在預賽的時候就落選了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很佩服她這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她什麼都會 可是卻一點都不驕矜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的推理能力更是沒得說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒有看到她拿手的檸檬派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在好像跟小蘭在烤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美明明說好要帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏漆抹黑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 真的是麻美你做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次做檸檬派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麻美你做的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我忘記把它帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 才會拜託小蘭來幫我做一個新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.02,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒做過怎麼做得好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.10,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 大家就先吃一口有什麼埋怨再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.29,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 味道真是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 看起來不怎樣不過味道真的不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 做菜重要的是內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以外表並不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吃看是不會知道味道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的推理可以說是百發百中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 就把這個案子給解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實破案的都是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我特地到銀座去訂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找火柴來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟澤井借了打火機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次在生日蛋糕上面點蠟燭的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管幾歲我都好興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種話 只會說到二十歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 一旦過了二十歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年只要增加一根蠟燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓你恨得要命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟預先說的一樣 剛剛十二點傳真就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我們借了一幢有傳真機的別墅是對的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來啦麻美 是高村教授的傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像已經睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 那這個蛋糕怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家待會不是還要去車站前唱卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 蛋糕就明天再吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個就先去唱卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 也只有這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:23.70,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}去把謎團解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.80,0:14:28.50,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}謎題即將解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 野口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會跟姐姐一塊合唱好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會唱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 下一首是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:46.30,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}只要唯一的願望可以實現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼鬱鬱寡歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.30,0:14:54.60,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來猜猜看 你在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才貌兼備 文武雙全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但體貼 大家又喜歡她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上不管做什麼事情都名列前茅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.10,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想麻美學姐的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為全都寫在你臉上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在訴說 我根本比不上人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一會喜歡她不是沒有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.70,0:15:17.70,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}為何我們兩人會相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.19,0:15:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她以前還是足球社裏的經理人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:26.50,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一起共看如此悽涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不用那麼在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人家已經把新一給甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個不是青梅竹馬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:34.30,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一最喜歡吃的是檸檬派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天聽麻美學姐說了才知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.50,0:15:39.00,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一他喜歡吃檸檬派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他最愛吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為他今天會到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才特地做檸檬派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來新一他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.80,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這樣吧 我來教你怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能贏過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學姐對新一的瞭解比我知道的太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:18.70,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭你也有自己的優點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你倒說說看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.20,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你練空手道練出一手好臂力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有全身充滿了肌肉不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數好像少了很多的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因為毛利先生一直不離開廁所的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都去車站前的廁所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的香煙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到隔壁的便利商店幫你買去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 野口人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子說想在車站逛一逛好讓酒趕快醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經三點多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客廳裏那麼紊亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家趕快回去收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是不是失火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.31,0:17:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那裏難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們租用的別墅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.90,0:17:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在那裏還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之大家先趕到別墅去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說不定還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車鑰匙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在野口身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼"怎麼回事"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們租用的別墅已經失火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 千萬不能有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 她根本沒有到外面避難的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還在裏面睡覺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要打電話叫醒她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就睡在客廳裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火已經燒到那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 根本進不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 別過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那邊的摩托車推走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若油箱被引燃就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.19,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全帽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就進去了 學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說小蘭跟柯南都進裏面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤井學長也進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.39,0:19:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 麻美學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去啊 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 我的女兒還在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也會有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別墅附近的醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是事後被抬過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 麻美學姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就躺在你旁邊的病床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然醫生說只有輕微的一氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過生命沒有大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 她終於得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 是小蘭你去救她的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得我一心要到屋裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了學姐之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤井學長就帶著我們到了安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們出來之後 突然鬆了口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就昏了過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你很厲害耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是帶著安全帽才進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防人員都這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們不贊成貿然闖進火場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過戴上安全帽是正確的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.41,0:20:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是柯南啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我昨天要進去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南把安全帽交給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.07,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說戴上安全帽可以保護頭髮跟臉不被火燒傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還真是一個不可思議的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起火時間是凌晨兩點五十分嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為住在別墅附近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經看到這一帶冒煙的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一開始以為只是營火沒有特別注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有蓄意縱火的跡象嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 火源是在客廳裏面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想引起火災的原因應該是這個蛋糕的蠟燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕的蠟燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.02,0:21:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他們大概是忘了把蠟燭吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好又掉到了地上的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好將散落在地上的禮品包裝紙燒了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.37,0:21:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後才會連窗簾也燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不把火給熄掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂說 我明明有熄掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.62,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家出門的時候都慌慌張張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經說我真的熄滅了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們發現那些蠟燭都已經燒到底部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是因為忘記熄火的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就只有一個可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.05,0:21:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是待在客廳裏的麻美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己又把蠟燭的火點上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.73,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
